      <p>
        All tax rates used in this calculator are sourced from official HMRC publications:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/income-tax-rates" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Income tax rates and personal allowances: GOV.UK</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/national-insurance-rates-letters" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">National Insurance rates and categories: GOV.UK</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/tax-on-bonus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tax on bonus payments: GOV.UK</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/rates-and-thresholds-for-employers-2026-to-2027" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Rates and thresholds for employers 2026/27: GOV.UK</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For a complete overview of all tax rates and thresholds this year, see our <a href="/guides/uk-tax-year-2026-27/">UK Tax Year 2026/27 guide</a>.
      </p>

    </article>
  </Fragment>
</CalculatorLayout>
